summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to zoning and land use; amending Plat 65E, page 158 of the official zoning map adopted by Ordinance 86300 (page 24-381, Seattle Municipal Code) to rezone certain property in Block 1, Brent's Street Addition to the City of Columbia and in Corliss Addition to Columbia from RS 5000 to RD 5000 (C.F. 2900468 - Petition of R.A. Swartout).
